Analysis
  Time Complexity
     Best Case: O(1) (when years = 0)
     Average Case: O(n)
     Worst Case: O(n)
  Space Complexity
     O(n) due to the recursive call stack.
Optimization
  Use Memoization to avoid repeated calculations.
  Use Dynamic Programming for improved efficiency.
  Use an Iterative Approach to reduce space complexity from O(n) to O(1).
